Package think.rpgitems.power.impl

Class Fire

  • java.lang.Object
    • think.rpgitems.power.BasePropertyHolder
      • think.rpgitems.power.impl.BasePower
        • think.rpgitems.power.impl.Fire
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Power, PropertyHolder
    public class Fire
extends BasePower
    Power fire.

    The fire power will fire an fireblock on right click that burns entities hit for duration in ticks. Furthermore it sends out a burning trail into the aimed direction for distance blocks.
